--time sc(0,9,9) s.drawTextBox(4, 18, 24, 13, string.format("%.0f", timeh24),-1,0) s.drawTextBox(4, 18, 24, 13, ":",0,0) s.drawTextBox(3, 18, 24, 13, string.format("%.0f", min),1,0) end

object.script:
s=screen s.dt=s.drawText i=input i.gn=i.getNumber s.sc=s.setColor
x=0 y=0 z=0 k=0 set1=0 set2=0 consumptHour=0 per100kph=0 fuel=0 absConsumptHout=0 consumptMin = 0 minToFill = 0 consumptSec = 0 time=1 function onTick()
speed = i.gn(11) fluidLvl = i.gn(12) capacity = i.gn(13) time = i.gn(14) distance = i.gn(15)
percent = fluidLvl / capacity
if distance == 1 then convert = 3.6 elseif distance == 2 then convert = 2.236936 elseif distance == 3 then convert = 1.943844 end
if x ~= 601 then x=x+1 y=y+fluidLvl z=z+fluidLvl end
if x == 300 then set1 = z/600 z=0 end
if x == 600 then set2 = y/600 consumptHour=math.floor((set1-set2)*720) per100kph = math.floor(consumptHour/((speed*convert)/100)) fuel = math.floor(set2) absConsumptHout = math.abs(consumptHour)
consumptMin=math.floor(math.abs((set1-set2)*12)) consumptSec=math.floor((math.abs((set1-set2)/5))*10)/10 minToFill = math.floor(math.abs((capacity-set2) / consumptMin)) x=0 y=0 end
if k ~= 1200 then k=k+1 end
inputX = i.gn(3) inputY = i.gn(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1)
isPressingRectangle = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, 0, 32, 12) output.setBool(1, isPressingRectangle)
end function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() if k == 1200 then
s.sc(10, 10, 10) s.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 27)
if isPressingRectangle then s.sc(20, 20, 20) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 33, 13) end
s.sc(10, 10, 10) s.drawRectF(3, 28, 26, 2) s.sc(10, 25, 4) --s.drawRectF(3, 28, percent*26, 2) s.drawRectF(3, 28, percent*18, 2)
s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.drawRectF(((x/600)*26)+2, 28, 2, 2)
s.sc(40, 40, 40) s.drawRect(2, 27, 27, 3) s.drawLine(0, 27, 32, 27)
s.sc(70, 70, 70) if time == 1 then s.dt(1, 1, " HOUR") elseif time == 2 then s.dt(1, 1, " MIN") elseif time == 3 then s.dt(1, 1, " SEC") end
s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 1, " >")
if consumptHour < -20 or consumptHour > 20 then if time == 1 then if absConsumptHout < 99999 then s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 7, absConsumptHout .. "L") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 7, absConsumptHout) else s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 7, math.floor(absConsumptHout/1000) .. "T") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 7, math.floor(absConsumptHout/1000)) end elseif time == 2 then if consumptMin < 99999 then s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 7, consumptMin .. "L") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 7, consumptMin) else s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 7, math.floor(consumptMin/1000) .. "T") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 7, math.floor(consumptMin/1000)) end elseif time == 3 then s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 7, consumptSec .. "L") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 7, consumptSec) end else s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(2, 7, "--") end s.sc(40, 40, 40) s.drawLine(0, 13, 32, 13)
s.sc(70, 70, 70) if consumptHour < -30 then s.dt(1, 15, "FILL") s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 21, minToFill.."m") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 21, minToFill)
else if convert == 3.6 then s.dt(1, 15, "100 KM") elseif convert == 2.236936 then s.dt(1, 15, "100 mi") elseif convert == 1.943844 then s.dt(1, 15, "100 Kt") end
if speed > 5 then if per100kph < 99999 then s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 21, per100kph.."L") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 21, per100kph) else s.sc(20, 20, 20) s.dt(1, 21, math.floor(per100kph/100) .."T") s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(1, 21, math.floor(per100kph/100)) end else s.sc(27, 70, 12) s.dt(2, 21, "--") end end
else s.drawTextBox(0, 7, 32, 5, "load", 0, 0) s.drawRect(2, 13, 27, 8) s.sc(12, 20, 70) s.drawRectF(3, 14, (k/1200)*25, 7) end end

object.script: function onTick() if init==nil then col=tonumber(property.getText("Background Color (RRGGBB)"),16) bb=col&0xff bg=(col>>8) & 0xff br=(col>>16) & 0xff btnUp=0 btnDown=0 btnEnter=0 duplex=false mode=0 timer=0 ch=prevCh(nextCh(property.getNumber("priority channel"))) curCh={ch,ch,16,ch} setCh(1,ch) port=property.getBool("Location") watch=property.getBool("Watch mode") and 3 or 2 extScan=property.getBool("Scan mode") timeout=5 init=true end enabled=input.getBool(4) if enabled then timer=timer+1 talk=input.getBool(6) fx=port and tx or rx strength=input.getNumber(32) btnUp=input.getBool(1) and btnUp+1 or 0 btnDown=input.getBool(2) and btnDown+1 or 0 btnEnter=input.getBool(3) and btnEnter+1 or 0 esc=btnEnter==1 and mode~=0 blt=input.getBool(5) if btnEnter==100 then timer=0 scanCh=curCh[2] mode=2 end if mode==1 then if talk then curCh[2]=curCh[1] mode=0 elseif esc then setCh(1,curCh[2]) mode=0 elseif timer%180==0 then setCh(1,curCh[timer/180%watch+2]) end if strength>.2 then timer=0 end elseif mode==2 then if strength>.2 then setCh(1,curCh[0]) mode=3 elseif timer%20==0 and extScan then setCh(0,16) elseif timer%10==0 then scanCh=nextCh(scanCh) setCh(0,scanCh) elseif talk then mode=0 elseif esc then setCh(1,curCh[2]) mode=0 end elseif mode==3 then if talk then curCh[2]=curCh[1] mode=0 elseif esc then setCh(1,curCh[2]) mode=0 elseif strength>.2 then timer=0 elseif timer>300 then mode=2 end else if talk then fx=port and rx or tx elseif btnUp%15==1 or (btnUp>80 and btnUp%5==1) then curCh[2]=nextCh(curCh[2]) setCh(1,curCh[2]) elseif btnDown%15==1 or (btnDown>80 and btnDown%5==1) then curCh[2]=prevCh(curCh[2]) setCh(1,curCh[2]) elseif btnEnter==1 then timer=0 mode=1 end end output.setNumber(1,fx) output.setBool(1,talk) else output.setBool(false) end end function onDraw() if enabled then screen.drawClear() screen.setColor(0,0,0,192) if mode==1 then screen.drawText(0,1,"WAT") screen.drawText(14,1,"CH") elseif mode>1 then screen.drawText(0,1,"SCAN") if mode==2 then screen.drawText(23,1,string.format("%02d",curCh[0])) end elseif talk then screen.drawText(3,1,"T") end if strength>0 then if mode==0 then screen.drawText(19,1,"R") end screen.drawLine(24,5,24,6) if strength>.25 then screen.drawLine(26,4,26,6) if strength>.5 then screen.drawLine(28,3,28,6) if strength>.75 then screen.drawLine(30,2,30,6) end end end end screen.drawText(0,16,"CH") draw7Seg(10,10,math.floor(curCh[1]/10)) draw7Seg(18,10,curCh[1]%10) screen.drawText(0,26,math.floor(fx/1000)) screen.drawText(14,26,".") screen.drawText(17,26,string.format("%03d",fx%1000)) screen.drawRectF(26,15,6,7) if blt then screen.setColor(br,bg,bb) else screen.setColor(48,64,48) end screen.drawText(27,16,duplex and "D" or "S") end end function nextCh(ch) return ch==28 and 60 or ch==69 and 71 or ch<88 and ch+1 or 1 end function prevCh(ch) return ch==60 and 28 or ch==71 and 69 or ch>1 and ch-1 or 88 end function setCh(i,ch) curCh[i]=ch dup=ch<6 or (ch>17 and ch<67) or (ch>77 and ch<86) tx=math.floor((ch<60 and 156000 or 153025)+ch*50+.5) rx=math.floor(dup and tx+4600.5 or tx+.5) fx=port and tx or rx if i==1 then duplex=dup end end function draw7Seg(x,y,i) if i~=1 and i~=4 then screen.drawLine(x+1,y,x+6,y) screen.drawLine(x+2,y+1,x+5,y+1) end if i<5 or i>6 then screen.drawLine(x+5,y+2,x+5,y+5) screen.drawLine(x+6,y+1,x+6,y+6) end if i~=2 then screen.drawLine(x+5,y+7,x+5,y+10) screen.drawLine(x+6,y+6,x+6,y+11) end if i~=1 and i~=4 and i~=7 then screen.drawLine(x+2,y+10,x+5,y+10) screen.drawLine(x+1,y+11,x+6,y+11) end if i==0 or i==2 or i==6 or i==8 then screen.drawLine(x,y+6,x,y+11) screen.drawLine(x+1,y+7,x+1,y+10) end if i<1 or i>3 and i~=7 then screen.drawLine(x,y+1,x,y+6) screen.drawLine(x+1,y+2,x+1,y+5) end if i>1 and i~=7 then screen.drawLine(x+2,y+5,x+5,y+5) screen.drawLine(x+2,y+6,x+5,y+6) end end

object.script:
si=math.sin co=math.cos pi=math.pi pi2=pi*2 s=screen ip=input
mx=gpsx my=gpsy zoom=1.5 zoomScale=zoom+zoom focusZone=false grid=250
function onTick() rx=ip.getNumber(1) ry=ip.getNumber(2) inputX=ip.getNumber(3) inputY=ip.getNumber(4) pressed=ip.getBool(1) and not isPressed--pulse isPressed=ip.getBool(1)
gpsx=ip.getNumber(10) gpsy=ip.getNumber(11)
compass=ip.getNumber(12)*pi2*-1 alt=ip.getNumber(13) if alt<0 then alt=0 end
zoomingIn=isPressed and iPIR(inputX,inputY,0,ry/5,6,ry/5) zoomingOut=isPressed and iPIR(inputX,inputY,0,ry/5*2,6,ry/5) reset=isPressed and iPIR(inputX,inputY,0,ry/5*3,6,ry/5)
if reset then focusZone=false zoom=1.5 grid=250 end if isPressed and inputX>6 then focusZone=true end if focusZone then if pressed and inputX>6 then tx,ty=map.screenToMap(mx,my,zoom,rx,ry,inputX,inputY) end cx,cy=map.screenToMap(mx,my,zoom,rx,ry,rx/2,ry/2) mx=cx+((tx-cx)*0.05) my=cy+((ty-cy)*0.05) else mx=gpsx my=gpsy end if zoomingIn and zoom>0.1 then zoomScale=zoom+zoom zoom=zoom-(zoomScale/100) end if zoomingOut and zoom<50 then zoomScale=zoom+zoom zoom=zoom+(zoomScale/100) end if zoom>0 and zoom<0.2 then grid=25 end if zoom>0.2 and zoom<0.5 then grid=50 end if zoom>0.5 and zoom<1 then grid=100 end if zoom>1 and zoom<2 then grid=250 end if zoom>2 and zoom<5 then grid=500 end if zoom>5 and zoom<10 then grid=1000 end if zoom>10 and zoom<20 then grid=2000 end if zoom>20 and zoom<40 then grid=4000 end if zoom>40 then grid=8000 end end function onDraw() w=s.getWidth() h=s.getHeight()
s.drawMap(mx,my+alt,zoom) s.setMapColorOcean(10,10,10) s.setMapColorShallows(15,15,15) s.setMapColorLand(50,50,50) s.setMapColorGrass(70,70,70) s.setMapColorSand(60,60,60) s.setMapColorSnow(60,60,60)
x1,y1=map.screenToMap(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,0,0) x2,y2=map.screenToMap(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,w,h) x1=math.floor(x1/grid)*grid y1=math.floor(y1/grid)*grid
s.setColor(0,0,0,20) for xx=x1,x2,grid do x,y = map.mapToScreen(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,xx,y1) screen.drawLine(x,0,x,h) end for yy=y1,y2,-grid do x,y = map.mapToScreen(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,x1,yy) screen.drawLine(0,y,w,y) end
dpsx,dpsy=map.mapToScreen(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,gpsx,gpsy) dpx,dpy=map.mapToScreen(mx,my,zoom,w,h,gpsx,gpsy) s.setColor(0,0,0,150) drawPointer(dpsx,dpsy+1,10,compass)--shadow s.setColor(255,255,255,60) s.drawLine(dpsx,dpsy,dpx,dpy)--line s.setColor(255,255,255) drawPointer(dpx,dpy,10,compass)
s.setColor(0,0,0,150) s.drawRectF(0,h/5,6,h/5*3)
if zoomingIn then s.setColor(255,255,255) else s.setColor(255,255,255,20)end s.drawTextBox(1,h/5,4,h/5,"+",0,0) if zoomingOut then s.setColor(255,255,255) else s.setColor(255,255,255,20)end s.drawTextBox(1,h/5*2,4,h/5,"-",0,0) if reset then s.setColor(255,255,255) else s.setColor(255,255,255,20)end s.drawTextBox(1,h/5*3,4,h/5,"r",0,0)
if not focusZone then if w>100 then s.setColor(0,0,0,150) s.drawLine(dpsx-6,dpsy-5,dpsx-10,dpsy-9) s.drawLine(dpsx+6,dpsy-5,dpsx+10,dpsy-9) s.drawLine(dpsx+6,dpsy+6,dpsx+10,dpsy+10) s.drawLine(dpsx-6,dpsy+6,dpsx-10,dpsy+10) s.setColor(255,255,255) s.drawLine(w/2-6,h/2-6,w/2-10,h/2-10) s.drawLine(w/2+6,h/2-6,w/2+10,h/2-10) s.drawLine(w/2+6,h/2+5,w/2+10,h/2+9) s.drawLine(w/2-6,h/2+5,w/2-10,h/2+9) end else x=dpx y=dpy L=h/6 s.setColor(255,255,255) s.drawRectF(w/2,h/2,1,1) if not iPIR(x,y,0,0,w,h) then x,y = w/2-x,h/2-y v = math.sqrt((x^2)+(y^2)) x,y = x/v,y/v s.drawLine(w/2-x*2,h/2-y*2-1,w/2-x*L,h/2-y*L-1) end end
s.setColor(255,255,255,30) s.drawRect(6,0,w-7,h-1) end
function iPIR(x,y,rX,rY,rW,rH) return x>rX and y>rY and x<rX+rW and y<rY+rH end function drawPointer(x,y,s,r,...) a=... a=(a or 30)*pi/360 x=x+s/2*si(r) y=y-s/2*co(r) screen.drawTriangleF(x,y,x-s*si(r+a),y+s*co(r+a),x-s*si(r-a),y+s*co(r-a)) end

object.script:
function onTick() p = input.getNumber(1) -- pitch angle ba1 = input.getNumber(2) -- bank angle inv = input.getNumber(3) -- inverted angle if inv>0 then -- check if artificial horizon should be upside down ba = ba1 elseif ba1>0 and inv<=0 then ba = 90+(90-ba1) elseif ba1<0 and inv<=0 then ba = -90+(-90-ba1) else ba = ba1 end end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() a1 = h/2 -- center height if w<65 then b1 = w/2 -- center width else b1 = (w/2)-10 end --p1 = p+a r = 1.5*w o = math.rad(ba) -- bank angle radians soh = math.sin(o) cah = math.cos(o) a = a1+(p*cah) -- center of rotation for horizon x value b = b1+(p*soh) -- center of rotation for horizon y value y1 = r*soh x1 = r*cah r2 = 90+(2*w) x2 = r2*soh y2 = r2*cah
screen.setColor(5, 20, 60) screen.drawTriangleF(-x1+b, y1+a, x1+b, -y1+a, -x2+b, -y2+a) -- sky screen.setColor(25, 10, 0) screen.drawTriangleF(-x1+b, y1+a, x1+b, -y1+a, x2+b, y2+a) -- ground screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) --screen.drawText(4, 4, p) -- displays pitch angle on screen --screen.drawText(4, 10, ba) -- displays bank angle on screen screen.drawLine(-x1+b, y1+a-cah, x1+b, -y1+a-cah) -- horizon
cx = -10*soh cy = -10*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 10 u cx = -20*soh cy = -20*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 20 u --screen.drawLine(b-4, p1+20, b+4, p1+20) -- 20 u cx = -30*soh cy = -30*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 30 u cx = -40*soh cy = -40*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 40 u cx = -50*soh cy = -50*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 50 u cx = -60*soh cy = -60*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 60 u cx = -70*soh cy = -70*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 70 u cx = -80*soh cy = -80*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 80 u
cx = 10*soh cy = 10*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 10 d --screen.drawLine(b - 4, p1 - 10, b + 4, p1 - 10) -- 10 d cx = 20*soh cy = 20*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 20 d cx = 30*soh cy = 30*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 30 d cx = 40*soh cy = 40*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 40 d cx = 50*soh cy = 50*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 50 d cx = 60*soh cy = 60*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 60 d cx = 70*soh cy = 70*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 70 d cx = 80*soh cy = 80*cah screen.drawLine((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) -- 80 d
screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) cxu1 = -86*soh cyu1 = -86*cah cxu2 = -94*soh cyu2 = -94*cah
cxd1 = 86*soh cyd1 = 86*cah cxd2 = 94*soh cyd2 = 94*cah screen.drawLine((-7*cah)+cxu1+b, (7*soh)+cyu1+a, (7*cah)+cxu2+b, (-7*soh)+cyu2+a) -- 90 degree X screen.drawLine((-7*cah)+cxu2+b, (7*soh)+cyu2+a, (7*cah)+cxu1+b, (-7*soh)+cyu1+a) screen.drawLine((-7*cah)+cxd1+b, (7*soh)+cyd1+a, (7*cah)+cxd2+b, (-7*soh)+cyd2+a) -- -90 degree X screen.drawLine((-7*cah)+cxd2+b, (7*soh)+cyd2+a, (7*cah)+cxd1+b, (-7*soh)+cyd1+a)
screen.setColor(255, 255, 0) screen.drawTriangleF(16, 16, 11, 21, 21, 21) -- center piece of artificial horizon screen.drawLine(b1-14, a1, b1-7, a1) screen.drawLine(b1+7, a1, b1+14, a1) end

function onTick() ap=gBl(1) labels=gBl(2)
heading=gNm(1) bug=gNm(2) end
function round(val,places,label) return string.format("%." .. (places or 0) .. "f", val) .. label end
function onDraw() --draw black band clr(0,0,0) rctF(0,0,32,2)
--draw heading tape for i=0,32,1 do if heading-(i-17) < 0 then headingOffset=360+heading-(i-17) elseif heading-(i-17) > 360 then headingOffset=heading-(i-17)-360 else headingOffset=heading-(i-17) end if headingOffset%10 == 0 then clr(f,f,f) rctF(32-i,0,2,1) end
--determine heading bug position t=(bug-heading+540)%360-180
if t < -17 then headingBugPos=0 elseif t > 15 then headingBugPos=30 else if headingOffset == bug or ((headingOffset == 0 or headingOffset == 360) and (bug == 0 or bug == 360)) then headingBugPos = 32-i end end end
--draw pointer clr(f,f,0) rctF(15,0,2,1)
--determine what to be displayed if labels then if heading == 360 or heading == 0 then headingPrint = "N" elseif heading == 45 then headingPrint = "NE" elseif heading == 90 then headingPrint = "E" elseif heading == 135 then headingPrint = "SE" elseif heading == 180 then headingPrint = "S" elseif heading == 225 then headingPrint = "SW" elseif heading == 270 then headingPrint = "W" elseif heading == 315 then headingPrint = "NW" else headingPrint = round(heading,0,"") end else headingPrint = round(heading,0,"") end
--draw black box clr(0,0,0) if string.len(headingPrint) == 2 then boxOffset=-3 elseif string.len(headingPrint) == 3 then boxOffset=-5 else boxOffset=0 end printOffset=(string.len(headingPrint)-1)*-2.5 --keep text centered rctF(13+boxOffset,2,6-2*printOffset,5)
--draw heading clr(f,f,f) txt(14+printOffset,2,headingPrint)
--draw heading bug if ap then clr(21,200,238) lne(headingBugPos-1,0,headingBugPos+3,0) lne(headingBugPos,1,headingBugPos+2,1) end end

gNm=input.getNumber gBl=input.getBool sBl=output.setBool
clr=screen.setColor f=255 txt=screen.drawText rct=screen.drawRect rctF=screen.drawRectF lne=screen.drawLine tri=screen.drawTriangleF
feet=true
speedTapeScale=13 --pixels per 1000 units
function onTick() --multiply meters my unitMulti to convert unit unitMulti=gNm(8)
apEnabled=gBl(2) apGround=gBl(3) alt=gNm(5)*unitMulti vs=gNm(6)*3.28084*60 altSelect=gNm(7)*unitMulti-5 maxVs=gNm(9) end
function round(val,places,label) return string.format("%." .. (places or 0) .. "f", val) .. label end
function onDraw() --altitude tape clr(f,f,f) lne(2,0,2,32) for i=0,32,1 do altOffset=alt-((i-15)*(1000/speedTapeScale)) altThousands=tonumber(round(altOffset,0,"")) altCheck=tonumber(round(altThousands % 1000,0,"")) if alt-((32-15)*(1000/speedTapeScale)) > altSelect then altBugPos=32 elseif alt-((0-15)*(1000/speedTapeScale)) < altSelect then altBugPos=0 elseif (altOffset-altSelect) < (1000/speedTapeScale) and (altOffset-altSelect) > -(1000/speedTapeScale) then altBugPos=i end if altOffset < 1 then clr(f,0,0) lne(3,i,6,i) elseif altCheck < 1000/speedTapeScale then lne(3,i,6,i) lne(3,i-(speedTapeScale/2),4,i-(speedTapeScale/2)) lne(3,i+(speedTapeScale/2),4,i+(speedTapeScale/2)) txt(7,i-2,round(altOffset/1000,0,"")) end end
--vertical Speed Tape clr(f,0,f) lne(0,16,0,15-((vs/maxVs)*16)) lne(1,16,1,15-((vs/maxVs)*16))
--altitude lable clr(0,0,0) rctF(6,12,32,7) if alt < -1 then clr(f,0,0) else clr(f,f,f) end txt(7,13,round(alt,0,"")) clr(255,255,0) tri(1,13,1,19,5,16) lne(0,13,0,18)
--altitude bug if apEnabled then clr(21,200,238) tri(2,altBugPos-3,2,altBugPos+3,5,altBugPos) end
--Ground AP Indicator
if apGround then txt(14,20,"Gnd") end
end

gNm=input.getNumber gBl=input.getBool sBl=output.setBool
clr=screen.setColor f=255 txt=screen.drawText rct=screen.drawRect rctF=screen.drawRectF lne=screen.drawLine tri=screen.drawTriangleF
knots=true
speedTapeScale=1 --pixels per unit
accelDamp=false accel=0 accelPrint=0 accelSens=40 --lower is more sensitive maxAccel=15 --meters per second squared
function onTick() blnk=gBl(1) speed=gNm(5) Vs=gNm(7) Va=gNm(8) Vne=gNm(9)
--dampen acceleration to prevent erraticity if not accelDamp then accelLast=accel end accel=gNm(6)*60 if accel>accelLast+(maxAccel/(accelSens)) and accelPrint < maxAccel then accelDamp=true accelPrint=accelLast+(maxAccel/(accelSens)) accelLast=accelPrint elseif accel<accelLast-(maxAccel/(accelSens)) and accelPrint > -maxAccel then accelDamp=true accelPrint=accelLast-(maxAccel/(accelSens)) accelLast=accelPrint elseif accel<accelLast-(maxAccel/(accelSens)) or accel>accelLast+(maxAccel/(accelSens)) then accelDamp=true accelPrint=accelLast else accelDamp=false accelPrint=accel end end
function round(val,places,label) return string.format("%." .. (places or 0) .. "f", val) .. label end
function onDraw() --airspeed tape clr(f,f,f) lne(29,0,29,32) for i=-2,34,1 do speedOffset=tonumber(round(speed,0,""))-((i-15)/speedTapeScale) speedCheck=tonumber(round(speedOffset % 10,0,"")) if speedOffset < 0 then clr(f,0,0) lne(28,i,25,i) elseif speedCheck < 1 then clr(f,f,f) lne(28,i,25,i) txt(26-(string.len(round(speedOffset,0,""))*5),i-2,round(speedOffset,0,"")) elseif speedOffset-1 < Vs and speedOffset+1 > Vs then clr(f,0,0) lne(28,i,25,i) end if speedOffset > Vne then clr(f,0,0) rctF(29,i,1,1) elseif speedOffset > Va then clr(f,195,11) rctF(29,i,1,1) elseif speedOffset > Vs then clr(0,f,0) rctF(29,i,1,1) end end
--acceleration tape clr(f,0,f) lne(31,16,31,15-((accelPrint/maxAccel)*16)) lne(30,16,30,15-((accelPrint/maxAccel)*16))
--speed lable clr(0,0,0) rctF(0,12,26,7) if speed > Vne and blnk then clr(f,0,0) else clr(f,f,f) end txt(26-(string.len(round(speed,0,""))*5),13,round(speed,0,"")) clr(255,255,0) tri(31,13,31,19,27,16) rctF(29,13,1,1)--fixing the darn triangle because draw functions are inconsistent lne(27,15,31,12) lne(27,15,31,18) lne(31,13,31,18) end
